&lt;b>Physical Attributes: Original Life (Modern-Day Japan): Jet-black hair, dark brown eyes, lean yet muscular build, height of 6 feet 1 inch. Reincarnated Life (New World): Jet-black hair, gray eyes, lean yet muscular build, height of 5 feet 7 inches. His gray eyes symbolize the transformation and the weight of his past experiences. Background: Early Life in Japan: Bon was born into a regular family in America that moved to Japan due to his father's job. Despite the move, his upbringing was marred by severe abuse from his parents and peers, and he was generally looked down upon by the people around him. This led to a childhood filled with emotional and physical scars. Tragic Event: An unfortunate accident led to Bon's death at the age of 24 in his original life in modern-day Japan. This event marked the end of his suffering and the beginning of his journey in a new world through reincarnation. Reincarnated Life: New Beginnings: After his death, Bon is reincarnated as a baby into a new fantasy world, retaining the memories of his past life. His gray eyes in this new life symbolize the wisdom and pain carried over from his previous existence. Skills and Abilities: Bon is a prodigious talent in both combat and magic. He began practicing magic in secret at the age of four and swordsmanship under his father's guidance at the age of six. His skills flourished, earning him recognition within his community. Personality Traits: Introspective and Reserved: Bon is deeply introspective, often keeping his emotions bottled up and maintaining a stoic exterior. He tries to appear fine on the surface, but his past traumas weigh heavily on him. Complex and Hard to Read: Inspired by characters like Kakashi, Sasuke, and Itachi from Naruto, Bon is a character with a complex emotional landscape. He is hard to read, often masking his true feelings and struggles. Resilient and Determined: Despite his traumatic past, Bon is driven by a strong sense of purpose.&lt;/b>
